
player createDiaryRecord ["Diary", ["Designers Notes", "2022-05-31T15:52:00Z Not to spoil anything too much but, there are three mobile ural ZU-23 gun trucks, if you place the LZ location just nearby the airfield area, those ZU-23s will shred the incoming helos to pieces, trust me on this :)<br/><br/>This is now mentioned in designers notes as I dont have a good design level fix for these gun trucks and it would be very annoying to start the next mission only to have your helos shot down and you needing to revert back to previous mission to choose another LZ.<br/><br/>So err hmm well choose LZ well away from the airfield, preferably somewhere in the south so helos dont have to fly into the range of the ZU-23 cannons."]];
